##############################################

DOCUMENT();

loadMacros(
  "PGstandard.pl",
  "MathObjects.pl",
  "PGML.pl",
  "PGcourse.pl"
);

##############################################

Context("Numeric");

$a=random(11,19,1);
$b=random(51,59,1);

Context("LimitedNumeric");
$ans1 = Compute($a/100);
$ans2 = Compute($b/100);

##############################################

TEXT(beginproblem());

BEGIN_PGML

Change the following percentages into decimals:

    [`` [$a]% = ``] [_______]{$ans1}

    [`` [$b]% = ``] [_______]{$ans2}

END_PGML

##############################################

BEGIN_PGML_SOLUTION

To change a percentage to a decimal, we move the decimal point to the left twice.

    [`` [$a]% = [$ans1] ``]

    [`` [$b]% = [$ans2] ``]

END_PGML_SOLUTION

ENDDOCUMENT();


